{
  "video_id": "b64qvG2Jgro",
  "title": "Molly Crockett: Beware neuro-bunk",
  "es": 1,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 0.0,
      "end_time": 7000.0,
      "text": "Translator: Joseph Geni Reviewer: Morton Bast"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 16930.0,
      "end_time": 19970.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m a neuroscientist, and I study decision-making."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 19970.0,
      "end_time": 22276.0,
      "text": "I do experiments to test how different chemicals"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 22277.0,
      "end_time": 25877.0,
      "text": "in the brain influence the choices we make."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 25877.0,
      "end_time": 32625.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m here to tell you the secret to successful decision-making:"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 32625.0,
      "end_time": 34863.0,
      "text": "a cheese sandwich."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 34863.0,
      "end_time": 38522.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s right. According to scientists, a cheese sandwich"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 38523.0,
      "end_time": 42145.0,
      "text": "is the solution to all your tough decisions."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 42145.0,
      "end_time": 47202.0,
      "text": "How do I know? I&#39;m the scientist who did the study."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 47202.0,
      "end_time": 49501.0,
      "text": "A few years ago, my colleagues and I were interested"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 49502.0,
      "end_time": 51795.0,
      "text": "in how a brain chemical called serotonin"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 51795.0,
      "end_time": 55650.0,
      "text": "would influence people&#39;s decisions in social situations."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 55650.0,
      "end_time": 58160.0,
      "text": "Specifically, we wanted to know how serotonin would affect"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 58160.0,
      "end_time": 61974.0,
      "text": "the way people react when they&#39;re treated unfairly."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 61975.0,
      "end_time": 63513.0,
      "text": "So we did an experiment."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 63513.0,
      "end_time": 66658.0,
      "text": "We manipulated people&#39;s serotonin levels by giving them"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 66659.0,
      "end_time": 71282.0,
      "text": "this really disgusting-tasting artificial lemon-flavored drink"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 71282.0,
      "end_time": 74914.0,
      "text": "that works by taking away the raw ingredient for serotonin"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 74914.0,
      "end_time": 76920.0,
      "text": "in the brain."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 76920.0,
      "end_time": 79690.0,
      "text": "This is the amino acid tryptophan."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 79690.0,
      "end_time": 81430.0,
      "text": "So what we found was, when tryptophan was low,"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 81430.0,
      "end_time": 83882.0,
      "text": "people were more likely to take revenge"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 83882.0,
      "end_time": 87430.0,
      "text": "when they&#39;re treated unfairly."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 87430.0,
      "end_time": 91253.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s the study we did, and here are some of the headlines"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 91253.0,
      "end_time": 93982.0,
      "text": "that came out afterwards."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 93982.0,
      "end_time": 96477.0,
      "text": "(\"A cheese sandwich is all you need for strong decision-making\")"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 96477.0,
      "end_time": 98572.0,
      "text": "(\"What a friend we have in cheeses\")"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 98572.0,
      "end_time": 101772.0,
      "text": "(\"Eating Cheese and Meat May Boost Self-Control\") At this point, you might be wondering, did I miss something?"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 101772.0,
      "end_time": 107167.0,
      "text": "(\"Official! Chocolate stops you being grumpy\") Cheese? Chocolate? Where did that come from?"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 107167.0,
      "end_time": 109300.0,
      "text": "And I thought the same thing myself when these came out,"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 109300.0,
      "end_time": 113545.0,
      "text": "because our study had nothing to do with cheese or chocolate."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 113545.0,
      "end_time": 115874.0,
      "text": "We gave people this horrible-tasting drink"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 115874.0,
      "end_time": 119760.0,
      "text": "that affected their tryptophan levels."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 119760.0,
      "end_time": 122756.0,
      "text": "But it turns out that tryptophan also happens to be found"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 122757.0,
      "end_time": 125558.0,
      "text": "in cheese and chocolate."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 125558.0,
      "end_time": 127868.0,
      "text": "And of course when science says cheese and chocolate"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 127868.0,
      "end_time": 131948.0,
      "text": "help you make better decisions, well, that&#39;s sure to grab people&#39;s attention."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 131949.0,
      "end_time": 133916.0,
      "text": "So there you have it:"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 133916.0,
      "end_time": 137423.0,
      "text": "the evolution of a headline."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 137423.0,
      "end_time": 139765.0,
      "text": "When this happened, a part of me thought, well,"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 139765.0,
      "end_time": 141768.0,
      "text": "what&#39;s the big deal?"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 141769.0,
      "end_time": 145648.0,
      "text": "So the media oversimplified a few things, but in the end,"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 145648.0,
      "end_time": 147724.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s just a news story."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 147724.0,
      "end_time": 151770.0,
      "text": "And I think a lot of scientists have this attitude."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 151770.0,
      "end_time": 154974.0,
      "text": "But the problem is that this kind of thing happens all the time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 154974.0,
      "end_time": 158101.0,
      "text": "and it affects not just the stories you read in the news"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 158101.0,
      "end_time": 160880.0,
      "text": "but also the products you see on the shelves."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 160880.0,
      "end_time": 163547.0,
      "text": "When the headlines rolled, what happened was,"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 163547.0,
      "end_time": 166373.0,
      "text": "the marketers came calling."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 166373.0,
      "end_time": 169591.0,
      "text": "Would I be willing to provide a scientific endorsement"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 169592.0,
      "end_time": 172853.0,
      "text": "of a mood-boosting bottled water?"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 172853.0,
      "end_time": 174997.0,
      "text": "Or would I go on television to demonstrate,"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 174997.0,
      "end_time": 176220.0,
      "text": "in front of a live audience,"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 176220.0,
      "end_time": 179620.0,
      "text": "that comfort foods really do make you feel better?"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 179621.0,
      "end_time": 183582.0,
      "text": "I think these folks meant well, but had I taken them up on their offers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 183582.0,
      "end_time": 185956.0,
      "text": "I would have been going beyond the science,"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 185956.0,
      "end_time": 189213.0,
      "text": "and good scientists are careful not to do this."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 189213.0,
      "end_time": 193581.0,
      "text": "But nevertheless, neuroscience is turning up more and more in marketing."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 193581.0,
      "end_time": 196141.0,
      "text": "Here&#39;s one example: Neuro drinks,"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 196141.0,
      "end_time": 199382.0,
      "text": "a line of products, including Nuero Bliss here,"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 199382.0,
      "end_time": 202283.0,
      "text": "which according to its label helps reduce stress,"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 202283.0,
      "end_time": 205708.0,
      "text": "enhances mood, provides focused concentration,"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 205709.0,
      "end_time": 208397.0,
      "text": "and promotes a positive outlook."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 208397.0,
      "end_time": 213220.0,
      "text": "I have to say, this sounds awesome. (Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 213220.0,
      "end_time": 216898.0,
      "text": "I could totally have used this 10 minutes ago."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 216898.0,
      "end_time": 220328.0,
      "text": "So when this came up in my local shop, naturally I was"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 220328.0,
      "end_time": 223877.0,
      "text": "curious about some of the research backing these claims."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 223877.0,
      "end_time": 226803.0,
      "text": "So I went to the company&#39;s website looking to find"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 226803.0,
      "end_time": 230228.0,
      "text": "some controlled trials of their products."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 230229.0,
      "end_time": 231906.0,
      "text": "But I didn&#39;t find any."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 231906.0,
      "end_time": 235644.0,
      "text": "Trial or no trial, these claims are front and center"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 235644.0,
      "end_time": 239606.0,
      "text": "on their label right next to a picture of a brain."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 239606.0,
      "end_time": 245309.0,
      "text": "And it turns out that pictures of brains have special properties."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 245309.0,
      "end_time": 247771.0,
      "text": "A couple of researchers asked a few hundred people"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 247771.0,
      "end_time": 250462.0,
      "text": "to read a scientific article."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 250462.0,
      "end_time": 253789.0,
      "text": "For half the people, the article included a brain image,"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 253789.0,
      "end_time": 255652.0,
      "text": "and for the other half, it was the same article"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 255652.0,
      "end_time": 258356.0,
      "text": "but it didn&#39;t have a brain image."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 258356.0,
      "end_time": 259988.0,
      "text": "At the end — you see where this is going —"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 259988.0,
      "end_time": 262980.0,
      "text": "people were asked whether they agreed"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 262980.0,
      "end_time": 265420.0,
      "text": "with the conclusions of the article."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 265420.0,
      "end_time": 267693.0,
      "text": "So this is how much people agree with the conclusions"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 267693.0,
      "end_time": 269606.0,
      "text": "with no image."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 269606.0,
      "end_time": 273253.0,
      "text": "And this is how much they agree with the same article"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 273253.0,
      "end_time": 276200.0,
      "text": "that did include a brain image."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 276200.0,
      "end_time": 277969.0,
      "text": "So the take-home message here is,"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 277969.0,
      "end_time": 282876.0,
      "text": "do you want to sell it? Put a brain on it."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 282876.0,
      "end_time": 284989.0,
      "text": "Now let me pause here and take a moment to say that"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 284989.0,
      "end_time": 288686.0,
      "text": "neuroscience has advanced a lot in the last few decades,"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 288687.0,
      "end_time": 291140.0,
      "text": "and we&#39;re constantly discovering amazing things"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 291140.0,
      "end_time": 292413.0,
      "text": "about the brain."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 292413.0,
      "end_time": 295557.0,
      "text": "Like, just a couple of weeks ago, neuroscientists at MIT"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 295557.0,
      "end_time": 298357.0,
      "text": "figured out how to break habits in rats"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 298357.0,
      "end_time": 302350.0,
      "text": "just by controlling neural activity in a specific part of their brain."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 302350.0,
      "end_time": 303940.0,
      "text": "Really cool stuff."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 303940.0,
      "end_time": 307233.0,
      "text": "But the promise of neuroscience has led to some really"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 307233.0,
      "end_time": 312469.0,
      "text": "high expectations and some overblown, unproven claims."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 312469.0,
      "end_time": 315508.0,
      "text": "So what I&#39;m going to do is show you how to spot"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 315508.0,
      "end_time": 319540.0,
      "text": "a couple of classic moves, dead giveaways, really,"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 319540.0,
      "end_time": 321849.0,
      "text": "for what&#39;s variously been called neuro-bunk,"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 321850.0,
      "end_time": 327542.0,
      "text": "neuro-bollocks, or, my personal favorite, neuro-flapdoodle."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 327542.0,
      "end_time": 331880.0,
      "text": "So the first unproven claim is that you can use brain scans"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 331880.0,
      "end_time": 335792.0,
      "text": "to read people&#39;s thoughts and emotions."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 335792.0,
      "end_time": 338839.0,
      "text": "Here&#39;s a study published by a team of researchers"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 338839.0,
      "end_time": 341672.0,
      "text": "as an op-ed in The New York Times."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 341672.0,
      "end_time": 345917.0,
      "text": "The headline? \"You Love Your iPhone. Literally.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 345917.0,
      "end_time": 350366.0,
      "text": "It quickly became the most emailed article on the site."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 350367.0,
      "end_time": 352536.0,
      "text": "So how&#39;d they figure this out?"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 352536.0,
      "end_time": 355564.0,
      "text": "They put 16 people inside a brain scanner"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 355564.0,
      "end_time": 358846.0,
      "text": "and showed them videos of ringing iPhones."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 358846.0,
      "end_time": 362308.0,
      "text": "The brain scans showed activation in a part of the brain"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 362308.0,
      "end_time": 364960.0,
      "text": "called the insula, a region they say"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 364960.0,
      "end_time": 368744.0,
      "text": "is linked to feelings of love and compassion."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 368744.0,
      "end_time": 372404.0,
      "text": "So they concluded that because they saw activation in the insula,"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 372404.0,
      "end_time": 376691.0,
      "text": "this meant the subjects loved their iPhones."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 376691.0,
      "end_time": 378835.0,
      "text": "Now there&#39;s just one problem with this line of reasoning,"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 378835.0,
      "end_time": 382351.0,
      "text": "and that&#39;s that the insula does a lot."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 382351.0,
      "end_time": 384656.0,
      "text": "Sure, it is involved in positive emotions"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 384656.0,
      "end_time": 386998.0,
      "text": "like love and compassion,"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 386998.0,
      "end_time": 389671.0,
      "text": "but it&#39;s also involved in tons of other processes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 389671.0,
      "end_time": 392744.0,
      "text": "like memory, language, attention,"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 392744.0,
      "end_time": 396780.0,
      "text": "even anger, disgust and pain."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 396780.0,
      "end_time": 401243.0,
      "text": "So based on the same logic, I could equally conclude"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 401243.0,
      "end_time": 403695.0,
      "text": "you hate your iPhone."
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 403696.0,
      "end_time": 406540.0,
      "text": "The point here is, when you see activation in the insula,"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 406540.0,
      "end_time": 409566.0,
      "text": "you can&#39;t just pick and choose your favorite explanation"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 409566.0,
      "end_time": 414232.0,
      "text": "from off this list, and it&#39;s a really long list."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 414232.0,
      "end_time": 416566.0,
      "text": "My colleagues Tal Yarkoni and Russ Poldrack"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 416566.0,
      "end_time": 419688.0,
      "text": "have shown that the insula pops up in almost a third"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 419688.0,
      "end_time": 424424.0,
      "text": "of all brain imaging studies that have ever been published."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 424424.0,
      "end_time": 425938.0,
      "text": "So chances are really, really good"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 425938.0,
      "end_time": 429630.0,
      "text": "that your insula is going off right now,"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 429640.0,
      "end_time": 430686.0,
      "text": "but I won&#39;t kid myself"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 430686.0,
      "end_time": 434363.0,
      "text": "to think this means you love me."
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 434363.0,
      "end_time": 437270.0,
      "text": "So speaking of love and the brain,"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 437270.0,
      "end_time": 441135.0,
      "text": "there&#39;s a researcher, known to some as Dr. Love,"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 441135.0,
      "end_time": 444620.0,
      "text": "who claims that scientists have found the glue"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 444620.0,
      "end_time": 447267.0,
      "text": "that holds society together,"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 447267.0,
      "end_time": 451430.0,
      "text": "the source of love and prosperity."
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 451430.0,
      "end_time": 453232.0,
      "text": "This time it&#39;s not a cheese sandwich."
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 453232.0,
      "end_time": 457890.0,
      "text": "No, it&#39;s a hormone called oxytocin."
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 457890.0,
      "end_time": 458956.0,
      "text": "You&#39;ve probably heard of it."
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 458956.0,
      "end_time": 461848.0,
      "text": "So, Dr. Love bases his argument on studies showing"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 461848.0,
      "end_time": 464793.0,
      "text": "that when you boost people&#39;s oxytocin,"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 464793.0,
      "end_time": 468966.0,
      "text": "this increases their trust, empathy and cooperation."
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 468966.0,
      "end_time": 473460.0,
      "text": "So he&#39;s calling oxytocin \"the moral molecule.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 473460.0,
      "end_time": 475888.0,
      "text": "Now these studies are scientifically valid,"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 475888.0,
      "end_time": 480240.0,
      "text": "and they&#39;ve been replicated, but they&#39;re not the whole story."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 480240.0,
      "end_time": 482737.0,
      "text": "Other studies have shown that boosting oxytocin"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 482737.0,
      "end_time": 487480.0,
      "text": "increases envy. It increases gloating."
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 487480.0,
      "end_time": 490796.0,
      "text": "Oxytocin can bias people to favor their own group"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 490796.0,
      "end_time": 493888.0,
      "text": "at the expense of other groups."
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 493888.0,
      "end_time": 498140.0,
      "text": "And in some cases, oxytocin can even decrease cooperation."
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 498140.0,
      "end_time": 501960.0,
      "text": "So based on these studies, I could say oxytocin"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 501960.0,
      "end_time": 506710.0,
      "text": "is an immoral molecule, and call myself Dr. Strangelove."
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 506711.0,
      "end_time": 510710.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 510710.0,
      "end_time": 514181.0,
      "text": "So we&#39;ve seen neuro-flapdoodle all over the headlines."
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 514181.00000000006,
      "end_time": 516959.00000000006,
      "text": "We see it in supermarkets, on book covers."
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 516957.99999999994,
      "end_time": 519629.99999999994,
      "text": "What about the clinic?"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 519630.0,
      "end_time": 523440.0,
      "text": "SPECT imaging is a brain-scanning technology"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 523440.00000000006,
      "end_time": 525113.0,
      "text": "that uses a radioactive tracer"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 525114.0,
      "end_time": 528154.0,
      "text": "to track blood flow in the brain."
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 528154.0,
      "end_time": 531238.0,
      "text": "For the bargain price of a few thousand dollars,"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 531238.0,
      "end_time": 535356.0,
      "text": "there are clinics in the U.S. that will give you"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 535356.0,
      "end_time": 538809.0,
      "text": "one of these SPECT scans and use the image"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 538809.0,
      "end_time": 541445.0,
      "text": "to help diagnose your problems."
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 541446.0,
      "end_time": 543975.0,
      "text": "These scans, the clinics say, can help"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 543975.0,
      "end_time": 546877.0,
      "text": "prevent Alzheimer&#39;s disease,"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 546877.0,
      "end_time": 549341.0,
      "text": "solve weight and addiction issues,"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 549341.0,
      "end_time": 552130.0,
      "text": "overcome marital conflicts,"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 552130.0,
      "end_time": 555163.0,
      "text": "and treat, of course, a variety of mental illnesses"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 555163.0,
      "end_time": 558742.0,
      "text": "ranging from depression to anxiety to ADHD."
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 558742.0,
      "end_time": 561312.0,
      "text": "This sounds great. A lot of people agree."
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 561312.0,
      "end_time": 563478.0,
      "text": "Some of these clinics are pulling in tens of millions"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 563478.0,
      "end_time": 566781.0,
      "text": "of dollars a year in business."
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 566782.0,
      "end_time": 568866.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s just one problem."
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 568866.0,
      "end_time": 571543.0,
      "text": "The broad consensus in neuroscience"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 571543.0,
      "end_time": 574728.0,
      "text": "is that we can&#39;t yet diagnose mental illness"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 574728.0,
      "end_time": 577511.0,
      "text": "from a single brain scan."
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 577511.0,
      "end_time": 579742.0,
      "text": "But these clinics have treated"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 579742.0,
      "end_time": 582182.0,
      "text": "tens of thousands of patients to date,"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 582182.0,
      "end_time": 583944.0,
      "text": "many of them children,"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 583944.0,
      "end_time": 587421.0,
      "text": "and SPECT imaging involves a radioactive injection,"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 587422.0,
      "end_time": 593419.0,
      "text": "so exposing people to radiation, potentially harmful."
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 593419.0,
      "end_time": 596533.0,
      "text": "I am more excited than most people, as a neuroscientist,"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 596533.0,
      "end_time": 600814.0,
      "text": "about the potential for neuroscience to treat mental illness"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 600814.0,
      "end_time": 605538.0,
      "text": "and even maybe to make us better and smarter."
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 605538.0,
      "end_time": 608238.0,
      "text": "And if one day we can say that cheese and chocolate"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 608238.0,
      "end_time": 612542.0,
      "text": "help us make better decisions, count me in."
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 612542.0,
      "end_time": 615118.0,
      "text": "But we&#39;re not there yet."
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 615118.0,
      "end_time": 618853.0,
      "text": "We haven&#39;t found a \"buy\" button inside the brain,"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 618853.0,
      "end_time": 622550.0,
      "text": "we can&#39;t tell whether someone is lying or in love"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 622551.0,
      "end_time": 625934.0,
      "text": "just by looking at their brain scans,"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 625934.0,
      "end_time": 630198.0,
      "text": "and we can&#39;t turn sinners into saints with hormones."
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 630198.0,
      "end_time": 632401.0,
      "text": "Maybe someday we will, but until then,"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 632402.0,
      "end_time": 635245.0,
      "text": "we have to be careful that we don&#39;t let overblown claims"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 635245.0,
      "end_time": 638631.0,
      "text": "detract resources and attention away from the real science"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 638631.0,
      "end_time": 642390.0,
      "text": "that&#39;s playing a much longer game."
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 642390.0,
      "end_time": 644828.0,
      "text": "So here&#39;s where you come in."
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 644828.0,
      "end_time": 647999.0,
      "text": "If someone tries to sell you something with a brain on it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 647999.0,
      "end_time": 650878.0,
      "text": "don&#39;t just take them at their word."
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 650878.0,
      "end_time": 654124.0,
      "text": "Ask the tough questions. Ask to see the evidence."
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 654124.0,
      "end_time": 658220.0,
      "text": "Ask for the part of the story that&#39;s not being told."
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 658220.0,
      "end_time": 663110.0,
      "text": "The answers shouldn&#39;t be simple, because the brain isn&#39;t simple."
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 663110.0,
      "end_time": 667605.0,
      "text": "But that&#39;s not stopping us from trying to figure it out anyway."
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 667605.0,
      "end_time": 671605.0,
      "text": "Thank you. (Applause)"
    }
  ]
}